description:
After drinking at home with Murakami, his best friend from university, Minowa woke up to find Murakami riding him. Tempted by the erotic expression on Murakami's face, Minowa unconsciously extended his hand&hellip;

&quot;You don't have to do anything. Just be good and lie down.&quot;

Put in this appealing situation, Minowa's best friend, who's cuter than any woman, unexpectedly forbids touching! Above all, he's the only one who knows the real Murakami, seen as a cool genius in university. Isn't it impossible not to have any feelings for him after being in that sort of situation?!

&quot;Even I want to make you feel good!&quot;

However, there's a reason why Murakami stubbornly rejects Minowa's touch; one that he doesn't want Minowa to find out no matter what.

Nagato Hiroki got drunk in college and made a mistake one night with a guy he'd never met. He's learned his lesson from the humiliation of being taken by a man and changed to a plainer image so that he isn't recognized by that man in case they ever meet again. Since becoming a working man, Hiroki hasn't been drinking or playing around, resigning himself to a serious and quiet existence. However, one day, he realizes that the high-powered man assigned from the head office as his new boss is that man, Kurosawa Naoya &ndash; and his peaceful, ordinary life takes a sudden turn. Kurosawa says he's been looking for him, and though Hiroki desperately tries to deny it, he's confronted with proof that they slept together: a mole in an intimate area that even he didn't even know about&hellip;?!

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Śmierć ojca, długi oraz porzucenie przez dziewczynę wpędziło Hirokiego w objęcia przypadkowego mężczyzny. Aby zapomnieć o tym upokorzeniu, zmienia sw&oacute;j image i z imprezowicza przekształca się w pilnego ucznia. Po czterech latach, gdy już myśli, że zaczyna wychodzić na prostą, znowu na horyzoncie pojawia się nieznajomy sprzed czterech lat&hellip;

What in everything you have ever thought about is doomed?
The Age of Gods is over. The Age of Human has come. The magic was lost in centuries but now it has turned into the greatest curse which leads to eternity. A Witch with silver hair. Her crimson eyes. Sounds of lyre. The Man in a Mask. An ill daughter. Young girls. Women. The story of the end, the story of the beginning in the same time. The story between two heavens. Another horizon covered with unforgiven sins and vain prays.
Where is the real heaven? The answer is beyond the ends&hellip;

Humans are always evolving. The ones who evolved in the right path would embody superpower, and called the &quot;White.&quot; However, the when their psyche can't keep up with the evolution of their body, they'll lose their mind and go berserk. They are called the &quot;Black.&quot;
Jin is a part of Black Line; the security company against the Black.
Jin swears to eliminate all the &quot;Black&quot; from this world&ndash;&ndash; weather by finding a cure to end the spread of the &quot;Black,&quot; or with his own fist and power.

The door to hell can only be opened by authorized personnel, and Takimura has found he is one of them. The problem is, he's still alive! Every workday Takimura is greeted by none other than the King of Hell himself, Enma. And everyday he asks Takimura the same question: &quot;Have you decided to become mine yet?&quot;

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Ono Takimura od trzech lat pracuje w biurze rządu. Gdy jego szef przechodzi na emeryturę, to właśnie on dostaje pracę w Piekle. Niewiarygodnie opanowany Ono niespecjalnie przejmuje się swoim nowym zakresem obowiązk&oacute;w, ale kiedy ciężkie, stoickie piekielne zasady zaczynają mieć na niego coraz większy wpływ, jego niezłomność kruszeje. Ponadto Ono zaczyna rozwijać zdolności wyczuwania ludzi, kt&oacute;rzy niebawem umrą&hellip;

Curiosity led Luo Wei to explore the forbidden cave on his school grounds. There, he discovered a pair of mysterious twins fleeing a plague. Little did he know that the cave is a portal to another world &mdash; things are not as simple as the twins make them out to be&hellip;

*There is no twincest in this.

Please read from left to right.

The enormous cave system, known as the Abyss, is the last unexplored place in the world. Nobody knows how deep down goes this titanic pit, inhabited by strange and wondrous creatures and full of mysterious ancient relics which purpose in unknown to modern man. Generations of bold adventurers have been drawn by the cryptic depths of the Abyss. In course of time those brave enough to explore the dangerous pit came to be known as &quot;Delvers.&quot;

In Orth, the town at the edge of the Abyss, there lives a little orphan named Riko, who dreams of becoming as great a delver as her mother was and solving the great mystery of the pit. One day, exploring the murky depths, she stumbles upon a little boy who turns out to be a robot&hellip;


[u][*]Nominated for the 11th Manga Taisho Awards in 2018.[/u]
